Package: meetube
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: YouTube client for Nokia N9
 A standalone YouTube client for the Nokia N9 (MeeGo Harmattan). Browse the home
 feed, search, watch videos with comments and related videos, sign in, and open
 channels. Ships its own OpenSSL 1.0.2, libpng12/libjpeg/libwebp, a WebP image
 plugin and a CA bundle under /opt/meetube so it runs on the stock device.
